58\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_custom_heading text=\"GENERAL TRANSPORTATION\" font_container=\"tag:h3|text_align:left\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1476668450319{margin-bottom: 23px !important;}\"][/vc_custom_heading][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1476671395942{padding-bottom: 24px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" list_style=\"list-arrow-right\" css=\".vc_custom_1476671291901{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]Freight and freight management are unique to each company’s specific needs and objectives across and affecting many factors.  We don’t expect you to adapt to our systems and methods. We build a solution to support you and your customers every day on every load.  We are biased toward solving your freight movement.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" list_style=\"list-arrow-right\" css=\".vc_custom_1476671299952{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]Serving our customers through changes in economic, market and regulatory conditions has taught us one thing…customers are looking for reliability. Determine method of shipment, and prepare bills of lading, invoices, and other shipping documents. Estimate freight or postal rates, and record shipment costs and weights.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1476671352438{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner][vc_separator color=\"custom\" accent_color=\"#dddddd\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1476671436254{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner][cms_download_file title=\"Download Our Service Brochures\" files=\"%5B%7B%22file_icon_class%22%3A%22fa%20fa-file-pdf-o%22%2C%22file_name%22%3A%22Download.PDF%22%2C%22file_link%22%3A%22%23%22%7D%2C%7B%22file_icon_class%22%3A%22fa%20fa-file-powerpoint-o%22%2C%22file_name%22%3A%22Download.PPT%22%2C%22file_link%22%3A%22%23%22%7D%5D\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1476671583008{padding-bottom: 25px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" list_style=\"list-arrow-right\" css=\".vc_custom_1476668917374{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_single_image image=\"560\" img_size=\"full\" css=\".vc_custom_1476671493157{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"TRANSPORTATION SERVICES\" font_container=\"tag:h3|text_align:left\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1476668767827{margin-bottom: 23px !important;}\"][/vc_custom_heading][vc_column_text]We are MOST<strong> </strong>biased towards Real People helping Real People.  You will not get a computer prompt asking you to press “1” for customer service.[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\n<ul>\n 	<li>Brokerage services</li>\n 	<li>Asset based services</li>\n 	<li>Logistic services</li>\n 	<li>Door to door delivery</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1476668924989{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_single_image image=\"561\" img_size=\"full\" css=\".vc_custom_1476671501498{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"PRETRANSPORT SERVICES\" font_container=\"tag:h3|text_align:left\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1476668784153{margin-bottom: 23px !important;}\"][/vc_custom_heading][vc_column_text]Pretransport service  is a premier logistics and transportation service provider. Our customized solutions, powered by our experienced staff, innovative technology.\n\nThe reliable equipment provide you with the confidence you need to focus on your business while we focus on your transportation.\n\nOur customers know that we provide Performance for the enterprises or suppliers.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Warehousing', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'warehousing', '', '', '2016-10-14 06:38:21', '2016-10-14 06:38:21', '', 0, 'http://tn.j