1476502109943{margin-bottom: 23px !important;}\"][/vc_custom_heading][vc_column_text]Sea freight, also known as ocean freight, is one of the longest established forms of transporting goods internationally. It\'s also one of the most economical. While <a class=\"link\" href=\"http://www.transglobalexpress.co.uk/air-freight/\">air freight</a> is favoured for time-sensitive shipments, sea freight is still the first choice for many businesses and individuals looking for a cost-effective solution.\n\nWhy not find out how much you could save by filling in the quote form above? Getting a quote is free, with no obligation to register or book.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1476502797658{margin-bottom: 44px !important;padding-top: 6px !important;}\"][vc_single_image image=\"542\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1476502502493{margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]Small businesses and individual customers may not typically consider sea freight as a viable option, as it tends to be associated with larger companies exporting high volumes of commercial cargo. But <a class=\"link\" href=\"http://www.transglobalexpress.co.uk/sea-freight/services/\">sea freight services</a> can also be a great option for transporting personal effects.\n\nWith our LCL (part container load) service, you don’t need to have enough cargo to fill a whole container in order to get a beneficial shipping rate.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1476505148839{margin-bottom: 37px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1476502512313{margin-bottom: 50px !important;padding-top: 6px !important;}\"][vc_single_image image=\"546\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1476502526847{margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]Small businesses and individua